{
  "id": "5a65a024de8d16001429f77e",
  "title": "クローズドなコミュニティの運営",
  "created": 1516609577,
  "updated": 1539025341,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5a65a024de8d16001429f77e",
      "text": "クローズドなコミュニティの運営",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609577,
      "updated": 1516609594
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a07baff09e0000649bd4",
      "text": " 秘密レベル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609659,
      "updated": 1516609664
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a074aff09e0000649bcf",
      "text": "  会の存在自体が秘密。会の存在についてNDA",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609653,
      "updated": 1516609734
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a074aff09e0000649bd0",
      "text": "  会の存在は公開だが参加者は秘密。参加者についてNDA",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609653,
      "updated": 1516609739
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a0a6aff09e0000649bd6",
      "text": "  話された内容に関してNDA",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609702,
      "updated": 1516609703
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a0e9aff09e0000649bd7",
      "text": "  [チャタムハウスルール]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609769,
      "updated": 1516610514
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a0eaaff09e0000649bd8",
      "text": "  \tチャタムハウス＝王立国際問題研究所、イギリスのシンクタンク",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609771,
      "updated": 1516609846
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a143aff09e0000649bd9",
      "text": "   チャタムハウスルール \"When a meeting, or part thereof, is held under the Chatham House Rule, participants are free to use the information received, but neither the identity nor the affiliation of the speaker(s), nor that of any other participant, may be revealed\".",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609859,
      "updated": 1516609878
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a143aff09e0000649bda",
      "text": "    当該会議で得られた情報を自由に利用できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609860,
      "updated": 1516610658
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a464aff09e0000649be7",
      "text": "    \tQ: 利用には引用・公開を含むのか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610661,
      "updated": 1539025213
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a532aff09e0000649bed",
      "text": "\t     A: [本家ページ https://www.chathamhouse.org/about/chatham-house-rule]によればこのルールの目的には\"to encourage openness and the sharing of information\"が含まれるので引用・公開を含む",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610866,
      "updated": 1539025198
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a17daff09e0000649bdc",
      "text": "    その情報の発言者やその他の参加者の身元および所属に関して秘匿しなければならない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609917,
      "updated": 1516610632
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a447aff09e0000649be6",
      "text": "    Q: 自分がその会に参加したことは公開してもよい？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610632,
      "updated": 1539025243
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a46baff09e0000649be8",
      "text": "    \tA: 引用の際に出典は言及するだろうから自分が参加していたことは公開されることになるな。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610667,
      "updated": 1539025260
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbba994aff09e0000f855dc",
      "text": "     \t「他の参加者を公開してはいけない」というルールなので、自分が参加していたことを公開するのはOK",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539025300,
      "updated": 1539025341
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a18daff09e0000649bdd",
      "text": "   see [王立国際問題研究所 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%8B%E5%9B%BD%E9%9A%9B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%89%80]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609934,
      "updated": 1516609953
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a1e5aff09e0000649bdf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610022,
      "updated": 1516610022
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a07aaff09e0000649bd3",
      "text": "\t会のメンバー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609658,
      "updated": 1516610028
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a1ebaff09e0000649be0",
      "text": " \t自由参加はあり得ない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610028,
      "updated": 1516610034
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a1f3aff09e0000649be1",
      "text": "  固定することも一つの手",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610036,
      "updated": 1516610048
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a04aaff09e0000649bce",
      "text": "  紹介者責任制",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609611,
      "updated": 1516610049
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a3bfaff09e0000649be2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610495,
      "updated": 1516610495
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a3bfaff09e0000649be3",
      "text": "\tチャタムハウスルールのイベントを開催するにはどうすればよいか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610495,
      "updated": 1516610508
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a4b2aff09e0000649beb",
      "text": " \t日程が事前に決まっていなくて調整さんみたいなツールを使いたい場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610738,
      "updated": 1516610750
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a418aff09e0000649be5",
      "text": "  \tイベントの趣旨を説明して興味があるかどうか聞く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610585,
      "updated": 1516610750
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a483aff09e0000649be9",
      "text": "   興味があると答えた人にまず参加者に関するNDAを掛ける",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610691,
      "updated": 1516610751
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a48eaff09e0000649bea",
      "text": "   その上で日程調整",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610703,
      "updated": 1516610751
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a1d5aff09e0000649bde",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516610005,
      "updated": 1516610136
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a03eaff09e0000649bcd",
      "text": "[クローズド]な[コミュニティ]の運営",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609599,
      "updated": 1516609605
    },
    {
      "id": "5a65a033aff09e0000649bcc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1516609588,
      "updated": 1516609588
    }
  ]
}